Package: tuikr
Title: Download Data File And Database Urls from TUIK
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Emrah", "Er", email = "eer@eremrah.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download Data File And Database Urls from TUIK (Turkish Statistical Institute).
    Provides functions to extract statistical tables, databases, and geographic data
    from the TUIK web portal and geographic statistics portal.
